rows.label: qst103613_msg0002
rows.name:
We've received word from the
Invidian government that they
will hand over Senator Stol.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0003
rows.name:
His son was protected elsewhere
and will be taken care of at
a military facility.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0005
rows.name:
What kind of father puts his
child through such hardship...

rows.label: qst103613_msg0006
rows.name: It seems things will finally calm down.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0007
rows.name:
There are still those who
plot against the Empire?!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0009
rows.name:
I'm sorry... At the moment,
I don't have any information
that could be a lead...

rows.label: qst103613_msg0011
rows.name: Kagutsuchi! We must not give up!!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0012
rows.name:
We exist to protect this
Empire... and Neferu-sama!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0013
rows.name:
If we continue our journey,
we will surely catch their
tail somewhere!!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0014
rows.name:
You're quite hot-blooded for
someone who looks like you...

rows.label: qst103613_msg0016
rows.name:
Now, everyone! Let us go
and search for clues!
